oasted unsalted peanuts, cut into pieces, for garnishing"]}],"id":"r156355","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-nF4WElW9C2k\/XZMvx3X1geI\/AAAAAAAAaWA\/4ZYKOOOwPC4RyceQN10DvsqYkDqm7fbeACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_pU7GWbaVn1QXJtjR.png","title":"Steamed sticky rice with pork (Rice tube puddings)","publishedAt":"2017-05-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"12 g","fat":"5 g","uom":"per 1 cup","carbohydrates":"45 g","calories":"1163 kJ \/ 278 kcal"},"usefulItems":"dariole mould (5 x 5 cm), small bowl, bowl, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Dried small shrimp can be purchased in Asian grocers. You can omit them or replace them with shallots, for a different but pleasant result.<br>- Instead of dariole moulds, you can also use <nobr>7 heat-resistant<\/nobr> drinking glasses <nobr>(7 cm diameter,<\/nobr> <nobr>6 cm height).<\/nobr> In this case, increase water to <nobr>900 g<\/nobr> and steaming time to <nobr>50-55 minutes.<\/nobr> If your moulds or glasses are a different size than specified, you may need to adjust the steaming time."],"basicInfo":["medium","25m","2h 30m","10 cups"]}